;Default language victory quotes **MUGEN 1.0**
;The default language victory quotes must be implemented in English.

[Quotes]
victory1 = "Nah I win."
victory2 = "The only reason you were the strongest was because I wasnt born yet"
victory3 = "You did good, but not enough to win"
victory4 = "Too Weak, Too Slow, Too Easy"
victory5 = "Another one fails trying to defeat me"
victory6 = "I was holding back this whole fight"
victory7 = "You left stains on my clothing, dumbass"
victory8 = "Don't worry, I'm still the strongest."
